280→     * The PTY session behaves like a real terminal, supporting features like command history.
281→     *
282→     * @param {PtyCreateOptions & PtyConnectOptions} options - PTY session configuration including creation and connection options
283→     * @returns {Promise<PtyHandle>} PTY handle for managing the session
